source: TEXT_SUBSEA011_00121_SEQ_00<tab>Sisipu of the Fishermen's Guild wants to order a new fishing boat.
target: TEXT_SUBSEA011_00121_SEQ_00<tab>漁師ギルドのシシプは、新しい漁船を購入したいようだ。

source: TEXT_SUBSEA011_00121_SEQ_01<tab>Keen to take to the seas once more, Sisipu expresses her desire to have a new fishing boat built. She bids you consult with Forgemaster H'naanza of the Armorers' Guild in her stead regarding how long the commission might take.
target: TEXT_SUBSEA011_00121_SEQ_01<tab>漁師ギルドのシシプから、漁船の発注の伝言を頼まれた。甲冑師ギルドの「ハ・ナンザ」に申し出よう。

source: TEXT_SUBSEA011_00121_SEQ_02<tab>H'naanza regretfully informs you that Naldiq & Vymelli's is presently occupied with a large commission. Nonetheless, the forgemaster promises to do what she can in honor of the long-standing relationship between their two guilds.
target: TEXT_SUBSEA011_00121_SEQ_02<tab>甲冑師ギルドの「ハ・ナンザ」に、新しい漁船の発注を依頼した。ハ・ナンザによると、現在、ナルディク＆ヴィメリー社では大型船の建造中で忙しいようだ。しかし、漁師ギルドは上得意であるため、なんとかするとハ・ナンザは約束してくれた。

source: TEXT_SUBSEA011_00121_TODO_00<tab>Speak with H'naanza at the Armorers' Guild.
target: TEXT_SUBSEA011_00121_TODO_00<tab>甲冑師ギルドのハ・ナンザと話す

source: TEXT_SUBSEA011_00121_SISIPU_000_0<tab>The Calamity really knocked the wind out the fishing industry's sails, but fisherfolk are starting to return to the seas once more. It's past time I did the same.
target:
TEXT_SUBSEA011_00121_SISIPU_000_0第七霊災以降、漁をやめていた人たちが、
最近、徐々に海に戻ってきているわ。

source: TEXT_SUBSEA011_00121_SISIPU_000_1<tab>But before I can put out to sea again, I need to have a new boat built. Our guild has always commissioned Naldiq & Vymelli's for its crafts, but they are beastly busy these days.
target:
TEXT_SUBSEA011_00121_SISIPU_000_1でも、漁に出るには漁船が必要でしょ？
だから、ナルディク＆ヴィメリー社に
新しい漁船を発注したいのよね。

source: TEXT_SUBSEA011_00121_SISIPU_000_2<tab>If you want for something to do, mayhap you could run over to the Armorers' Guild and consult with Forgemaster H'naanza in my stead. I would know how long we might expect to have to wait.
target:
TEXT_SUBSEA011_00121_SISIPU_000_2あなた、上甲板層の甲冑師ギルドへひとっぱしりして
「ハ・ナンザ」さんへ、発注の件を伝えてみてくれない？
彼女が造船会社の社長さんなのよ。

source: TEXT_SUBSEA011_00121_HNAANZA_000_10<tab>A new boat for the Fishermen's Guild? I'm afraid now isn't the best time...
target:
TEXT_SUBSEA011_00121_HNAANZA_000_10なに、漁師ギルドが漁船を発注したいって！？
そりゃ、少々困ったね……

source: TEXT_SUBSEA011_00121_HNAANZA_000_11<tab>You see, we have recently taken on a commission for a galleon. This task alone has all our hands full.
target:
TEXT_SUBSEA011_00121_HNAANZA_000_11ナルディク＆ヴィメリー社は、
目下、大型船の建造で大忙しなんだ。
漁師ギルドの注文に応じるのは、かなり厳しいな……。

source: TEXT_SUBSEA011_00121_HNAANZA_000_12<tab>But look, I will see what I can do. The Fishermen's Guild has long been one of our best clients, and I would be loath to disappoint Sisipu. It may yet take a while, but I shall endeavor to have her boat ready in a timely fashion.
target:
TEXT_SUBSEA011_00121_HNAANZA_000_12でも、漁師ギルドは、昔からの上得意だからね。
なんとか期待に応えられるよう、努力すると、
シシプに伝えておくよ。
